0.1.name: wordpress/gigs-calendar
0.1.description: This plugin is geared toward bands and musicians to manage and display a calendar of their gigs within WordPress. It's meant to be as easy as possible for both the musician and the fan. It even manages venue data complete with mapping and ticket links.
